title: Malang | Privacy Policy
content: Malang | Privacy Policy Privacy Policy Effective Date: July 1, 2023 Malang – Fine Arts & Photography Club (“Malang,” “we,” “us,” or “our”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle any personal information you choose to share with us through our website and services. 1. Data Collection We do not collect any personal information unless you explicitly provide it—such as through forms or by sharing your email address voluntarily. 2. Use of Information If you provide your email address, we may use it to: Send club updates or newsletters. Share information about events, activities, or announcements. We will only use your email for the purpose it was provided. 3. Data Sharing We do not sell, share, or disclose your personal information to third parties.
